{"type":"question","id":14236,"title":"日本為什麼能成為世界上惟一一個接受且流行男性中/長髮的國家?","uid":13149,"topics":[4898,32],"contents":"華人文化圈不用說了,留個長髮別人在大街上別人以為你是流氓.大多數行業你留長髮去面試就肯定不招\\\\<br>\n東方也就韓國人愛留個鍋蓋頭,但服完兵役後一般都不再留長髮<br>\n歐美稍為好一點,一般對長髮沒特別大意見 但長髮在文職人員/高管/政府部門依然很少見<br>\n<br>\n其他伊斯蘭/印度/非洲更加少男性長髮<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n但在日本,留下圖這種程度的中長髮是非常普遍的(但不一定有電捲/用髮蠟)<br>\n起碼留個瀏海是極普遍的<br>\n<a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-KFtCl6PoFN0/UPwK8YT3MwI/AAAAAAAAAvU/Nxx_MaMWt6k/s320/japan-hairstyle-male-hair-cuts.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-KFtCl6PoFN0/UPwK8YT3MwI/AAAAAAAAAvU/Nxx_MaMWt6k/s320/japan-hairstyle-male-hair-cuts.jpg\" alt=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-KFtCl6PoFN0/UPwK8YT3MwI/AAAAAAAAAvU/Nxx_MaMWt6k/s320/japan-hairstyle-male-hair-cuts.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/twenty20/private_images/t_watermark-criss-cross-10/v1481756813000/photosp/be8fc727-955a-4a93-93cd-42fb13965ad8/stock-photo-people-street-crossing-zebra-crossing-crowd-crowded-group-pedestrians-pedestrian-crossing-be8fc727-955a-4a93-93cd-42fb13965ad8.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/twenty20/private_images/t_watermark-criss-cross-10/v1481756813000/photosp/be8fc727-955a-4a93-93cd-42fb13965ad8/stock-photo-people-street-crossing-zebra-crossing-crowd-crowded-group-pedestrians-pedestrian-crossing-be8fc727-955a-4a93-93cd-42fb13965ad8.jpg\" alt=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/twenty20/private_images/t_watermark-criss-cross-10/v1481756813000/photosp/be8fc727-955a-4a93-93cd-42fb13965ad8/stock-photo-people-street-crossing-zebra-crossing-crowd-crowded-group-pedestrians-pedestrian-crossing-be8fc727-955a-4a93-93cd-42fb13965ad8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n在大街上不難找到一堆留中/長髮但穿西裝打領帶的<br>\n甚至國會議員也有<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/1710143187/641\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/1710143187/641\" alt=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/1710143187/641\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n然後前首相小泉,不曉得是不是世界上惟一一個留長髮的領袖<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n然後日本式中/長髮,仿佛只適合日本人.&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n日本人留它不會有污穢,不專業,不成熟的感覺<br>\n同是東亞人的中國人一留就像個乞丐/鄉村非主流","date":"2019-12-28","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":4}